Linux From Scratch 9 \r (\l)

login:
    root : root

networking (wired):
    sed "s/eth0/<wired interface>/" -i /etc/sysconfig/ifconfig.wired
    ifup wired

networking (wifi):
    sed "s/wlan0/<wifi interface>/" -i /etc/sysconfig/ifconfig.wifi
    ifup wifi

project page:
    https://github.com/viyoriya/lfs-scripts
